<article class="post">
  <header class="post-header">
    <h1 class="post-title">{{ title }}</h1>
    <p class="post-meta">{{ page.date | date }}</p>
    {% if thumbnail %}
      <img class="post-hero" src="{{ thumbnail }}" alt="{{ title }}">
    {% endif %}
    {% if description %}
      <p class="post-desc">{{ description }}</p>
    {% endif %}
  </header>

  <div class="post-content">
    {{ content | safe }}
  </div>

  <aside class="cta-box">
    <h3>빠르게 안전하게 보내세요</h3>
    <p>UN 포장 · DGD 서류 대행 · DHL/FedEx 위험물 취급</p>
    <a class="btn" href="https://tosomelogis.com/contact">지금 상담하기</a>
  </aside>

  <p class="backlink"><a href="/">← 블로그 목록으로</a></p>
</article>

